Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.90,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji challenged the director\Nto a final gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:56.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは黒幕会長に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:56.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の勝負を挑んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:01:01.10,default,,0,0,0,,The director accepts,\Nbut only with three conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:01:01.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長は勝負の受諾と引き換えに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:01:01.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある提案をする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:04.51,default,,0,0,0,,One of them is\Na wager of 100 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:04.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは掛け金１億の勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジが賭けるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万と指４本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:09.11,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's wager comprises of\N20 million and four of his fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:13.82,default,,0,0,0,,100 million.\NA staggering amount!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:17.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:17.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的な金それが目の前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:17.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つかめば届く所にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:17.52,default,,0,0,0,,The money is before his eyes\Nand within his reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:37.64,default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:44.65,default,,0,0,0,,His fingers are at stake\Nif he loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:45.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ければ持っていかれるこの指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:49.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,根元から４本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:47.87,default,,0,0,0,,They will be excised at the root!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:53.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:53.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:53.34,default,,0,0,0,,So, what will it be, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:58.05,default,,0,0,0,,Not only will I lose my fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:59.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,指をなくす上に2000万も取られ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.67,default,,0,0,0,,but I'll lose\Nthe 20 million too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:02.69,default,,0,0,0,,All that will remain\Nare debts and pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残るのは借金と痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:05.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壊滅的敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.65,default,,0,0,0,,A complete utter defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ちの2000万が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みすぼらしく見えちまう大金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:09.16,default,,0,0,0,,That huge amount makes\Nmy 20 million look shabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:14.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時給900円の俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:14.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんだけ働いても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.59,default,,0,0,0,,With my hourly pay of 900 yen,\NI'll never attain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:20.18,default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I work.\NNo matter how hard I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,働いても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,働いても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,働いても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,働いても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:24.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たどり着けない金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.82,default,,0,0,0,,I'll never achieve that amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:28.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけあればやり直せる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:27.60,default,,0,0,0,,With this, I can start all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.60,default,,0,0,0,,I can start over from\Nthe beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:31.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:31.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:34.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の願い通りの人生にやり直せる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:34.56,default,,0,0,0,,I can rebuild my life again\Njust the way I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:39.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ　怖いのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:38.11,default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:39.45,default,,0,0,0,,The only thing to fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:42.17,default,,0,0,0,,...is if he draws the winning lot\Non the first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつが１回目に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりを引いてしまうこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:47.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありえないことじゃないが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:47.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限りなく０に近い確率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:46.73,default,,0,0,0,,It's not entirely impossible but\Nhe has almost no chance of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:50.44,default,,0,0,0,,As long as I don't get unlucky,\NI'm sure to win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな不運さえなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:52.21,default,,0,0,0,,I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:53.98,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.56,default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.44,default,,0,0,0,,- B-But!\N- It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.22,default,,0,0,0,,If you lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし負けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは考えないわけじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:03.06,default,,0,0,0,,It's true that it's not\Nentirely impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:07.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ける不運を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:07.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで考えないわけじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:07.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:06.22,default,,0,0,0,,It's not entirely impossible\Nto suffer bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:07.23,default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この俺の人生を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全に塗り替えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:11.82,default,,0,0,0,,I can repaint my life again\Nfrom scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:16.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけの金を目の前にして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.23,default,,0,0,0,,The money to do so\Nis right before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,降りられるか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.24,default,,0,0,0,,Can I let it pass by?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＧＯだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.24,default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.45,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Investment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＧＯだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は指を賭ける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.48,default,,0,0,0,,Go!\NI'll bet my fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:46.64,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, spoken like a\Nyoung man pursuing his dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでこそ夢を追う若者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,素晴らしい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.83,default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛んだぞ眠気が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.08,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sleepy anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:55.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかげで覚醒した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.35,default,,0,0,0,,I'm now fully awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:01.23,default,,0,0,0,,They're dancing,\Nmy aging cells are dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:04:01.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,踊る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:04:01.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この老いぼれの細胞が踊る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:05.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脳を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:05.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ベータエンドルフィンが駆け巡る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:05.57,default,,0,0,0,,My beta-endorphins are\Npumping madly within my brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,活性化する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.29,default,,0,0,0,,It's a revival!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.99,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'm truly grateful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これぞ長寿の秘訣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.46,default,,0,0,0,,This is the secret to longevity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:17.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:17.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:17.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしておる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.53,default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NGet started!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,用意だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.65,default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさとせんか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グズが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.07,default,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up, slow coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セット完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでもう動かせない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:51.26,default,,0,0,0,,Everything is ready!\NThere's no backing out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:56.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの左手は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:56.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,指先がわずかに動かせるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:55.51,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji can barely move\Nhis fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あはは　狂気の沙汰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.94,default,,0,0,0,,This is madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:03.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えてみればつくづく狂気の沙汰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:02.68,default,,0,0,0,,This is a state of madness,\Nhowever you look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.84,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうは思わんか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:08.26,default,,0,0,0,,We're betting on\Nfrail slips of paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:08.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吹けば飛ぶようなそんな紙くず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.36,default,,0,0,0,,...that would fly away\Nat the slightest breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:12.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,即席のそんなくじに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:12.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かたや１億
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.23,default,,0,0,0,,With a wager of\N100 million on one side...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:17.61,default,,0,0,0,,...and 20 million plus\Nfour fingers on the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かたや指４本と2000万を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賭けようというのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.17,default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it,\Nthis is bizarre!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:21.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いなく常軌を逸しておる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:29.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし快感は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:29.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当のめくるめく快感は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:29.52,default,,0,0,0,,But doing this feels\Ntruly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常軌を逸するからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たどり着ける
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.72,default,,0,0,0,,One can only feel like this\Nduring extreme situations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:38.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:38.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうそのことを知っておろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:38.97,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, I'm sure you've\Nexperienced it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:42.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.25,default,,0,0,0,,You crossed the bridge\Nand survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:47.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橋を渡りきっての生き残り
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:47.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｅカードの勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.98,default,,0,0,0,,You won in E-Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:50.73,default,,0,0,0,,That moment of\Nhappiness and relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:53.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その瞬間の歓喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:53.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安堵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:53.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,快感は強烈だったはず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.60,default,,0,0,0,,...must have been one\Nof heightened pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死の際の生は苦しくとも充実し
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:59.87,default,,0,0,0,,Near-death instances\Nare painful, but satisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:05.77,default,,0,0,0,,And the experience of surviving\Neach time is simply sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:07.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,またそこからの生還は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:07.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世のものとは思えぬほど甘美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:09.50,default,,0,0,0,,Absolute bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的至福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その快感に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうカイジ君の脳は焼かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:13.96,default,,0,0,0,,The experience of that pleasure\Nhas taken over your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:17.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:17.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これからのカイジ君の人生は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:17.25,default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you will\Nprobably live your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:22.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その快感を追い続ける人生になる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:21.41,default,,0,0,0,,...pursuing excitement\Nof that nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:27.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう意味では
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:27.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮にここで１億を手にしても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:27.11,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you win this match\Nto obtain 100 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.42,default,,0,0,0,,your addiction to that ecstasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:32.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いずれその快感に身を任せ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:32.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルの闇に消える金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.19,default,,0,0,0,,...would cause you to gamble\Nthat money away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがジャンキーの性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.72,default,,0,0,0,,That's the life of an addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あーははははは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.23,default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:44.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう懲り懲りさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:44.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな地獄めぐりはもう懲り懲り
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.37,default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.98,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of\Ngambling my life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はもしここで勝ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっちり足を洗う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:49.31,default,,0,0,0,,If I win, I'll wash my\Nhands off gambling completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこれが最後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:54.25,default,,0,0,0,,That's why this is the last...\NMy last gamble ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に最後のギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.49,default,,0,0,0,,I'll survive and return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう生還する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は生還する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:07:01.64,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to reclaim my life\Nfrom this never ending nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:02.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わらない悪夢から
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:08.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう　ふはは　はははははは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:11.35,default,,0,0,0,,Place the money\Non top of his 100 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金を置いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつの１億の上に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:12.81,default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,総額１億2000万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.00,default,,0,0,0,,A total sum of 120 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:21.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.98,default,,0,0,0,,- Hey...\N- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:23.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正確には2010万あって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.72,default,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's 20.1 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:26.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからその10万余分っていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:26.75,default,,0,0,0,,So, there's 100,000 extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:27.74,default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10万にとどまらねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.15,default,,0,0,0,,It won't just be 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:35.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:35.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆にはそれなりに配って回る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.75,default,,0,0,0,,If I win, I'll give everyone\Na substantial amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:38.34,default,,0,0,0,,You guys have helped me a lot,\Nespecially with the treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,治療やら何やら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろいろ世話になったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:43.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また世話になるかもしれんしの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:42.76,default,,0,0,0,,You'll probably\Nneed their help again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,治療やら何やら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:46.48,default,,0,0,0,,You'd need help\Nfor first aid, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:03.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ではそろそろ始めるかの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:03.51,default,,0,0,0,,Alright.\NShall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに積まれた１億
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が持って帰るか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:08.65,default,,0,0,0,,You'll either bring back the\N120 million from this gamble...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:12.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それともそれを果たせず
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:12.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,指を失うかもしれぬギャンブルを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.69,default,,0,0,0,,...or fail, and lose your\Nfingers as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待った
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.11,default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.14,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:36.28,default,,0,0,0,,Should we place that winning lot\Ninto the box together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:37.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その当たりくじだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:37.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人で入れようじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.38,default,,0,0,0,,I'd be in trouble if you\Nhid it elsewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:41.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入れたふりをして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:41.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかに忍ばされても困る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.12,default,,0,0,0,,...while pretending to put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:43.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬鹿な
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:43.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.48,default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!\NHe wouldn't stoop so low!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:46.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:46.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありうる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.74,default,,0,0,0,,No, that's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.86,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realise\Nuntil he said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言われりゃその通り
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ははは　では
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.22,default,,0,0,0,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.15,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待った
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじに触れる前に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.53,default,,0,0,0,,Before touching the lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その手に何も
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕込まれていないことを証明しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.87,default,,0,0,0,,you must prove that you've\Nnothing else in that hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはまた用心深い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:03.76,default,,0,0,0,,How wary of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:04.98,default,,0,0,0,,That goes without saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:09.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:09.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:09.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:09.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:08.48,default,,0,0,0,,Here. Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:10.26,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:12.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.38,default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あはは　ＯＫ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＯＫ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:16.91,default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.\NYou don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことせずとも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしゃカイジ君を信用しとるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.36,default,,0,0,0,,I trust you, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:25.76,default,,0,0,0,,Well then, now that neither\Nof us have a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では互いに問題のないところで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじを箱へ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:37.20,default,,0,0,0,,The winning ticket\Ngoes into the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,投入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.74,default,,0,0,0,,It is released!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ　では
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:52.44,default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.76,default,,0,0,0,,Will that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:02.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.49,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ではこちらのくじも入れます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:07.07,default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll place the\Nother lots inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,混ぜます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:13.00,default,,0,0,0,,Shuffling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これくらいなら落ちないはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.33,default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.52,default,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't cause it\Nto slip out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:29.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちなければ俺の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.79,default,,0,0,0,,If it didn't fall out, I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:33.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.02,default,,0,0,0,,As long as it doesn't slip out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:33.17,default,,0,0,0,,As long as it doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:44.27,default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. What he did wasn't\Nenough to make it slip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:44.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:44.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これくらいなら落ちない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.27,default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't fallen out.\NThe setup is still intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:48.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちていない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:48.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕込みは残っている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.20,default,,0,0,0,,After this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:55.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:55.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男が一発で引かなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:55.28,default,,0,0,0,,If he fails on\Nthe first attempt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:11:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ち　勝ち　勝ち　勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.78,default,,0,0,0,,I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.28,default,,0,0,0,,I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:10:59.87,default,,0,0,0,,I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:06.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ではまずわしから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:07.02,default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll be making\Nthe first draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:10.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１回目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:19.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.90,default,,0,0,0,,The director makes his pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,選択
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:25.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:25.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:23.81,default,,0,0,0,,Don't draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:25.77,default,,0,0,0,,Don't draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ともかくここ一度だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:30.28,default,,0,0,0,,Just draw a blank one.\NDon't draw the winning lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:33.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:33.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引かなければ勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.78,default,,0,0,0,,As long as he \Ndoesn't draw it, I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:34.80,default,,0,0,0,,I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:41.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えーと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:41.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこじゃろかい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.00,default,,0,0,0,,Where could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.00,default,,0,0,0,,Don't draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:45.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:45.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこじゃろかいな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.72,default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.27,default,,0,0,0,,Please, god!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:13.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:13.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレに残り
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:13.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他のティッシュ箱に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.86,default,,0,0,0,,At that time, No.5 who\Nremained in the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:17.29,default,,0,0,0,,...to dispose of the rest\Nof the lots, returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:18.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕込んだくじを処理した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:18.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５番も戻ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:21.16,default,,0,0,0,,But he's not the only one\Nto return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戻ってきたのは彼だけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼の後ろに十数人の男たち
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:24.44,default,,0,0,0,,About 10 other men\Nfollowed behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:29.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:29.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１番目の橋で落ちた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:29.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,重傷者たちである
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.16,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, they fell off\Nthe first bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.93,default,,0,0,0,,...and are now badly injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:34.21,default,,0,0,0,,Those watching Kaiji's game\Nsuffered less severe injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:34.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの戦いを見ていたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:34.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,比較的軽傷の者たちであった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,重傷者たちは部屋の外から
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中をうかがっていたのだが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:39.25,default,,0,0,0,,The others had been watching\Nfrom outside the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.77,default,,0,0,0,,but they now crawled forward\Nto Kaiji's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:43.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:43.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい進み
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:43.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジのそばに集まる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,共有するために
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.85,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they wanted a part\Nin this experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:49.68,default,,0,0,0,,A part of Kaiji's anxiety,\Nuncertainty and prayers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの不安と葛藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,祈り
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:56.19,default,,0,0,0,,And if he wins,\Nthey want to share his joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし勝ったならば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:57.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歓喜を共有するために
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えてみれば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジと彼らは皆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,似た者同士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:13:01.40,default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it, Kaiji is\Nin the same boat as them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:04.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆似たような過ちを犯し
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:06.62,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone made the same mistakes\Nand left behind a trail of debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多額の借金を背負い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現在は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はいつくばるような日々
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.41,default,,0,0,0,,They lead meaningless lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:13.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焦燥と失意と後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.44,default,,0,0,0,,They feel impatience,\Nlost and regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.31,default,,0,0,0,,They lead lives of distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦汁の日々
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.34,default,,0,0,0,,And they yearn\Nto be free again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこからの脱皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離脱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬間的離脱は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らの夢であり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:22.42,default,,0,0,0,,They dream of instant escape\Nfrom that way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.56,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最も分かりやすい形で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,達成されようとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:28.93,default,,0,0,0,,All that is now happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.96,default,,0,0,0,,...in the most\Nstraightforward way possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:36.21,default,,0,0,0,,If I win,\NI'll gain 120 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:36.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば 億　１億2000万
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:44.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:44.84,default,,0,0,0,,- Kaiji...\N- Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:44.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:44.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:44.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.70,default,,0,0,0,,If I win, I'll start afresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.95,default,,0,0,0,,Everything would have\Nbeen worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:50.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全てが報われる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.25,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:53.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:56.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.75,default,,0,0,0,,Sahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:01.46,default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'll be able\Nto rebuild my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:14:00.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてやり直せる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:02.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:08.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の人生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:08.53,default,,0,0,0,,My life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.02,default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:31.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おや
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.32,default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, oh my, oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:38.49,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, this is the most\Nfrightening part...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:40.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:40.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:40.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ一番の熱い勝負は恐ろしい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:40.76,default,,0,0,0,,...of a gambling match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:47.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,往々にして不可思議な
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:47.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず起こりえないことが起こる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.91,default,,0,0,0,,Now and then,\Nstrange occurences...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.77,default,,0,0,0,,...which should not occur\Nstart taking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常のはかりを超えてな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:50.17,default,,0,0,0,,It goes beyond\Nnormal calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:15:01.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.79,default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:15:01.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:15:01.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:59.86,default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me,\Nhe actually got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:04.01,default,,0,0,0,,He drew the winning lot\Nin just one try?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:04.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじを一発で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:13.53,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, this is the terrifying part\Nof a one-round gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:13.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが一発勝負の怖いところじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:16.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:16.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:16.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:15.30,default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:23.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きさま
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.77,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不思議じゃろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.31,default,,0,0,0,,Well? Mysterious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:33.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしのような王が一発で引けぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:32.90,default,,0,0,0,,Even a king like me couldn't\Ndraw it on my first attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:37.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな理不尽が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:37.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,起こってしまうのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:36.32,default,,0,0,0,,Such illogical things\Ndo occur...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:40.34,default,,0,0,0,,...in a one-round\Nmatch like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:40.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ一発の勝負では
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつふざけやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.81,default,,0,0,0,,He was mocking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:50.82,default,,0,0,0,,That was a deliberate attempt\Nto harrass me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,性質の悪い嫌がらせだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:55.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:55.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしのような王が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:55.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死にぞこないが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:54.86,default,,0,0,0,,What did that dotard mean\Nby "a king like me"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.34,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji curses the director\Ninwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:58.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:58.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心中で毒づく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがそんな怒りも一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.60,default,,0,0,0,,But his anger is only fleeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:04.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに別の圧倒的感情が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:04.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押し寄せてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:03.81,default,,0,0,0,,Soon, he will be overwhelmed\Nby a variety of other emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:10.12,default,,0,0,0,,He would be embraced with\Nrelief, great joy and happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安堵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歓喜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,至福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな思いが全身を包む
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:13.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:13.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引かなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.06,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, he did not draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:17.42,default,,0,0,0,,What matters is that the director\Ndid not draw the winning lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長は当たりくじを引かなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:18.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが全て
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:22.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:22.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう目前！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:21.43,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji could see his victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:25.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,片手じゃ持ちにくい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:25.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってくれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.82,default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to hold the box\Nwith one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.24,default,,0,0,0,,Could you hold it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:28.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.66,default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へへへ　どうぞどうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.67,default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:37.60,default,,0,0,0,,You get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:41.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が当たりを引いたら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:41.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おまえは派手に喜べ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:41.10,default,,0,0,0,,When I draw the winning lot,\Nyou'll make a big show of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱を引っちゃぶき
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:42.71,default,,0,0,0,,Tip the box upside down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:46.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中にあるもう１枚の当たりを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:46.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,床にばらまき
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:47.99,default,,0,0,0,,and scatter the remaining lot\Nwith those on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うやむやにする
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:53.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の左手が固定されている今
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:53.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはおまえの役目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:52.96,default,,0,0,0,,With my left hand strapped tight,\Nit's all up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.32,default,,0,0,0,,I got it, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってますってカイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:59.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの箱を持てって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:59.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言われた時から察してます
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:59.16,default,,0,0,0,,I understood the moment\NI was asked to hold the box...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:03.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:03.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,任せてください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.17,default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:04.70,default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:13.21,default,,0,0,0,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.93,default,,0,0,0,,With this... I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:17.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:20.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.18,default,,0,0,0,,With this,\NI'll get 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:22.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:28.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:28.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.86,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.22,default,,0,0,0,,That's strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじを仕込んだのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっち側だと思ってたが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.94,default,,0,0,0,,I remember putting the\Nfake lot on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないってことは逆だったか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手前か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.84,default,,0,0,0,,If it's not here, it must be\Non the other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:35.97,default,,0,0,0,,In front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.97,default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!\NWhere is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬鹿な
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして　そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:50.91,default,,0,0,0,,Why?! No way...\NIt's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:51.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことがあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:55.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり向こう側だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:55.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきはつい見つけ損ねただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:55.69,default,,0,0,0,,It must be on the other side!\NMaybe I overlooked it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:03.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:03.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奥か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:03.46,default,,0,0,0,,W-Why?!\NIs it further inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:09.07,default,,0,0,0,,Did I unknowingly push it\Nfurther in with my finger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:06.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき知らずに指で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:06.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:10.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奥に押し込んでしまったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:10.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.97,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:18.64,default,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:17.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:17.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:17.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:17.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ない！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちてしまったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:26.17,default,,0,0,0,,Did it fall while being\Nbrought here from the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:28.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきトイレから持ってきた時か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:28.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャッフルしている時に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.42,default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe during\Nthe shuffling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.19,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.20,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:58.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.71,default,,0,0,0,,I've no choice but to draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,九分九厘勝つギャンブルが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:02.06,default,,0,0,0,,My 99 percent sure-win gamble\Nhas become one of pure luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:05.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単なる運否天賦 五分五分の
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:05.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルになっちまったが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:04.64,default,,0,0,0,,It's now a 50-50 gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:07.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:07.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引けば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:09.87,default,,0,0,0,,But... if I manage to draw\Nthe winning lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:10.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ここで当たりを引けば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.22,default,,0,0,0,,I'll still be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうあれ助かる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:15.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:15.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかに必ず当たりが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:13.43,default,,0,0,0,,Because it's in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:17.23,default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely\Nsomewhere in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この中のどこかに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:21.97,default,,0,0,0,,I'll take hold of\Nthat luck right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:23.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その幸運を俺がここでつかむんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:23.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.74,default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.60,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:35.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えへ　えへへへへ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:38.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神よ！俺を祝福しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:38.22,default,,0,0,0,,Oh god, please grant me\Nthis blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:42.22,default,,0,0,0,,Save me! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救え！救うんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:19.89,default,,0,0,0,,But it failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.58,default,,0,0,0,,A second chance would\Ndo you no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:35.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２度はいかんな　あはははは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:39.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしのような王に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:39.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２度引かせてはいかん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:39.64,default,,0,0,0,,A king like myself should not be\Nallowed to draw a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:45.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２度もチャンスを与えられては
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:45.58,default,,0,0,0,,If you give me\Na second chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:49.84,default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to stop myself\Nfrom drawing the winning lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引きたくなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引いてしまうではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:57.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あは　いひひ　ひひひひひひひひ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:02.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,近づく夜明け
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.71,default,,0,0,0,,Daybreak approaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:07.10,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji isn't allowed to\Nawaken from his nightmare yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが悪夢はまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジに目覚めることを許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:12.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神はカイジと会長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:12.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どちらにほほ笑むのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:12.36,default,,0,0,0,,Will heaven smile upon Kaiji,\Nor the director?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:16.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの祈りは天に届くか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:16.00,default,,0,0,0,,Will Kaiji's prayers\Nascend to heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.58,default,,0,0,0,,Will they reach at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:19.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,届くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:45.81,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.45,0:22:46.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回｢残光｣
